*In the film [[Kappalottiya Thamizhan]], Actor Balaji played the role of Vanchinathan. Bharathiyar song "Kaattru veliyedai kannammma" was picturised with [[Gemini Ganesan]] and [[Savitri_(actress)|Savitri]]. [[Sivaji Ganesan]] played the role of [[V. O. Chidambaram Pillai]].
